text: Ærest on weale weg þonne on þa eorðburg<../images/tbar.gif>forð be wurtwalan to mearcwege þonne on wifeles ham westewearde<../images/tbar.gif>forð andlang burg beces þonne to wadleage westewearde.
Þonne to mearcwege<../images/tbar.gif>west to igfledwege on þa ac on fileðcumbe.
Þonne andlanges hagan on bidan ham eastewearde<../images/tbar.gif>andlanges hagan ut to Rodleage westewearde þonne to heaðfeldgeate.
